#: ../../../containers.rst:936
msgid "MPI"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:938
msgid ""
"Due to the dependency on Fortran for OpenMPI, which is the Spack default "
"implementation, consider adding ``gfortran`` to the ``apt-get install`` list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:940
msgid ""
"Recent versions of OpenMPI will require you to pass ``--allow-run-as-root`` "
"to your ``mpirun`` calls if started as root user inside Docker."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:942
msgid ""
"For execution on HPC clusters, it can be helpful to import the Docker image "
"into Singularity in order to start a program with an *external* MPI. "
"Otherwise, also add ``openssh-server`` to the ``apt-get install`` list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:946
msgid "CUDA"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:948
msgid ""
"Starting from CUDA 9.0, NVIDIA provides minimal CUDA images based on Ubuntu. "
"Please see `their instructions <https://hub.docker.com/r/nvidia/cuda/>`_. "
"Avoid double-installing CUDA by adding, e.g.:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:952
msgid ""
"packages:\n"
"  cuda:\n"
"    externals:\n"
"    - spec: \"cuda@9.0.176 arch=linux-ubuntu16-x86_64 %gcc@5.4.0\"\n"
"      prefix: /usr/local/cuda\n"
"    buildable: false"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:961
msgid "to your ``spack.yaml``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:963
msgid ""
"Users will either need ``nvidia-docker`` or, e.g., Singularity to *execute* "
"device kernels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:966
msgid "Docker on Windows and macOS"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:968
msgid ""
"On macOS and Windows, Docker runs on a hypervisor that is not allocated much "
"memory by default, and some Spack packages may fail to build due to lack of "
"memory. To work around this issue, consider configuring your Docker "
"installation to use more of your host memory. In some cases, you can also "
"ease the memory pressure on parallel builds by limiting the parallelism in "
"your ``config.yaml``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../containers.rst:972
msgid ""
"config:\n"
"  build_jobs: 2"
msgstr ""
